'''Elf Archers''' are rebel [[elf|elves]] found in [[Lletya]]. After completion of the [[Regicide]] [[quest]], [[slayer masters]] can assign them as a [[Slayer]] [[Slayer task|task]].{{CiteTwitter|author=Mod Ash|url=https://twitter.com/JagexAsh/status/713721069136449537|date=26 March 2016|archiveurl=https://archive.is/23AZX|archivedate=28 May 2020|quote=Elves: Regicide quest.}} They are usually killed on task or for [[teleport crystal]]s used to [[teleport]] to [[Lletya]] or, upon completion of [[Song of the Elves]], [[Prifddinas]].

